titleNullable: 2023 NWSL Womens Soccer League Player Stats FULL
subtitleNullable: Comprehensive player positions and stats for NWSL athletes - 2023
descriptionNullable:
2023 complete and comprehensive player stats for 347 NWSL athletes/players.
Data comes from NWSL.com. Data fields have been cleaned, and additional fields, like player position, have been added for NWSL data science fun.

Complete stats include:
- Attacking
- Passing
- Goals
- Defending
- PKs
- Goalkeeping

and more. 38 variables included. 

I have left NaNs in the dataset instead of filling them with 0s because 0 is a meaningful stat in this dataset. NaNs means there was no data available. For example, goalkeeping saves, 0 is a meaningful statistical number. But you can drop and clean NaNs for your own purposes on your own.

Percentages are in whole numbers.

2024 season stats and stadium attendance stats will be added soon. 

Message me for other women's sports ideas and variables to include.
